original: Lindahl, Ivar Vigilius, tandläkare, Virserum, f. 29/12/11 i Aseda, Kro-nob. L, av fabr. August L. o. Hanna Sahlin. G. 40 m. Zinela Wennerström. Barn: Ulf f. 41, Agne 45. — Stud:ex. i Växjö 30, tandl :kand. 33, tandläkare 36. Assist, v. Tandl :inst. protésavd. 36-37, assist, i Enskede 36-38, tjg. v. Röda Korsets ambuler. klinik i Jämtl. 38, praktik i Virserum sed. 39, assist :-tandl. v. Eastmaninst. 40-41. Led. av Virserums munic:fullm. sed. 43.
translated: Lindahl, Ivar Vigilius, dentist, Virserum, born on December 29, 1911 in Aseda, Kronoberg County, son of factory worker August L. and Hanna Sahlin. Married in 1940 to Zinela Wennerström. Children: Ulf, born in 1941, Agne, born in 1945. Completed high school in Växjö in 1930, dental studies in 1933, became a dentist in 1936. Worked as an assistant at the Dental Institute's prosthetic department from 1936-1937, in Enskede from 1936-1938, at the Red Cross mobile clinic in Jämtland in 1938, and established a practice in Virserum in 1939. Worked as an assistant dentist at the Eastman Institute from 1940-1941. Became a member of the Virserum municipal council in 1943.
